I don&rsquo;t particularly like HostGator as a company&hellip; Considering the inane 404 page they default your website to&hellip; But to remove that ad crap&hellip;
1. Download the .htaccess file from the root of your server&hellip;
2. Add the following lines (where /403.shtml can be any webpage you want to show for the specified error)
ErrorDocument 403 /403.shtmlErrorDocument 404 /404.shtmlErrorDocument 500 /500.shtml

3. Upload and overwrite .htaccess
http://support.hostgator.com/articles/cpanel/custom-error-pages
